FAIL_TO_PASS: when use collect example then option value resets
when env and cli defined then only parse value for cli
when option specified multiple times then callback called with value and previousValue
when option specified then value is as returned from callback
when optional with preset and coerce used then preset is coerced
when use increaseVerbosity example then option value resets
when variadic with coercion then coercion sets value
when env defined and no cli then custom parse from env
when commaSeparatedList x,y,z then value is [x, y, z]
when argument matches regexp then value is as specified
when collect -c a -c b -c c then value is [a, b, c]
when argument does not match regexp then value is default
